/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The vantage point is high, providing a bird's eye view of the urban landscape. The street, lined with trees and buildings, stretches out into the distance, creating a sense of depth and perspective. The buildings, predominantly white and gray, rise high into the clear blue sky, punctuated by a few wispy clouds. The sun shines brightly, casting a warm glow over the scene and creating a lens flare in the image. The colors are vibrant, with the green of the trees contrasting against the gray and white of the buildings. The image is taken from a low angle, which emphasizes the height of the buildings and the expanse of the sky.
